trans-unit.source: Represents a security token provider that provides <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken"></xref> security tokens for a SOAP message sender.
trans-unit.target: 代表安全性權杖提供者提供<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken"></xref>安全性權杖的 SOAP 訊息寄件者。

trans-unit.source: In most instances the KerberosSecurityTokenProvider class doesn't need to be called directly, as it is called when a client sends a SOAP message that requires a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken> security token.
trans-unit.target: 在大部分情況下 KerberosSecurityTokenProvider 類別不需要直接呼叫，因為當用戶端傳送 SOAP 訊息需要呼叫<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>安全性權杖。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: Specifically, a client specifies the type of security token needed using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenProvider.GetToken%2A> method to get a security token.
trans-unit.target: 具體而言，用戶端指定安全性權杖所需使用的型別<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>類別和<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>類別會呼叫<xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenProvider.GetToken%2A>方法來取得安全性權杖。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenProvider.GetToken%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>

trans-unit.source: When the security token needed is a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken> security token, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenProvider.GetToken%2A> method calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.KerberosSecurityTokenProvider.GetTokenCore%28System.TimeSpan%29> method.
trans-unit.target: 所需的安全性權杖時<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>安全性權杖<xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenProvider.GetToken%2A>方法呼叫<xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.KerberosSecurityTokenProvider.GetTokenCore%28System.TimeSpan%29>方法。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.KerberosSecurityTokenProvider.GetTokenCore%28System.TimeSpan%29> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SecurityTokenProvider.GetToken%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken>
